Example for:
luxury hotels in new york city
For some queries, such as luxury hotels in new york city, the available search parameters are different from the standard.

For this type of query, please note these functional differences:
It only accepts the limit parameter to adjust the number of results, and does not support pagination via offset.

This means it's not possible to retrieve subsequent pages of results; you can only request a larger set on the first page.

If Geographic Location parameters are used, the offset parameter becomes available; however, results may differ from those returned by the standard version of the query.

